Megatron sat back in Cyclonus' cockpit. He then leaned forward, over 
top of his comunicator. "Cyclonus, let us....talk," He seemed to be in 
rather good humor. "As I said before, I saw through Galvatron's eyes, 
since I was him, yet I didnt have the sense of time, or control. How 
long did you serve him?"
